data.description: Presenting an exquisite 1-story residence that encapsulates modern comfort and style, this home offers an array of amenities that cater to discerning individuals seeking a refined living experience within a thriving community governed by a Homeowners Association (HOA). Upon entering, you'll immediately appreciate the thoughtful design and spaciousness of the open floor plan. This home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, including a primary suite with an ensuite bathroom that's sure to impress. The ensuite features a separate garden tub and shower, double vanity, and a generously sized walk-in closet, providing a luxurious retreat within your own home. In addition to the primary suite, this home offers an office room, ideal for those who require a dedicated workspace or a quiet room for personal pursuits. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, complete with modern appliances, including a microwave, dishwasher, stove/range, and refrigerator. Preparing and enjoying meals has never been more convenient. For added functionality, the home includes a Jack and Jill full bathroom, perfect for accommodating guests or providing additional privacy for residents. The interior of this home showcases a blend of ceramic tile and vinyl flooring, offering both durability and aesthetic appeal. Low-maintenance and easy to clean, these flooring choices are ideal for those with a busy lifestyle. Step outside to the privacy-fenced backyard, where you can relax and unwind in seclusion. Whether you're looking to entertain guests or simply enjoy some outdoor solitude, this backyard offers the perfect setting. This rental property is located within an HOA that boasts an impressive array of amenities, including a playground, pool, tennis and basketball courts, and a clubhouse. These amenities provide endless opportunities for recreation, relaxation, and socializing with fellow residents.
